BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 163.92000000000002 740 Td (UNDERSTANDING EMOTIONAL DYSREGULATION) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 705 Td (Emotional dysregulation means your emotions are MORE INTENSE, come on) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 688 Td (FASTER, and take LONGER to return to baseline than other people's.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 671 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 654 Td (This is not a character flaw. It is a biological difference in how) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 637 Td (your nervous system processes emotional stimuli.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 620 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 603 Td (THE BIOSOCIAL THEORY:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 586 Td (  Biology: You were born with a more sensitive emotional system) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 569 Td (  + Environment: Your emotions were invalidated \('You're overreacting'\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 552 Td (  = Difficulty regulating emotions as an adult) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 535 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 518 Td (WHAT DYSREGULATION LOOKS LIKE:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 501 Td (  - Emotions go from 0 to 100 in seconds) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 484 Td (  - Small events trigger overwhelming reactions) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 467 Td (  - Difficulty calming down once upset) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 450 Td (  - Impulsive behaviors to escape pain \(spending, substances, self-harm\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 433 Td (  - Relationships feel all-or-nothing \(idealize/devalue\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 416 Td (  - Chronic feelings of emptiness) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 399 Td (  - Identity confusion \('Who am I really?'\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 382 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 365 Td (DBT teaches four skill sets to manage this:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 348 Td (  1. MINDFULNESS - Being present without judgment) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 331 Td (  2. DISTRESS TOLERANCE - Surviving crisis without making it worse) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 314 Td (  3. EMOTION REGULATION - Reducing vulnerability & changing emotions) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 297 Td (  4. INTERPERSONAL EFFECTIVENESS - Getting needs met in relationships) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
