BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 229.2 740 Td (WISE MIND MEDITATION) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 705 Td (Wise Mind is the overlap of EMOTION MIND and REASONABLE MIND.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 688 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 671 Td (EMOTION MIND: Ruled by feelings. Hot, reactive, impulsive.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 654 Td (REASONABLE MIND: Ruled by logic. Cold, rational, disconnected.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 637 Td (WISE MIND: Both. Intuitive knowing. Calm certainty.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 620 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 603 Td (MEDITATION SCRIPT 1: FINDING WISE MIND) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 586 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 569 Td (Close your eyes. Take three slow breaths.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 552 Td (Imagine walking down a spiral staircase, going deeper with each step.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 535 Td (At the bottom is a pool of still water - this is your Wise Mind.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 518 Td (Look into the water. What do you see? What do you know to be true?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 501 Td (Your Wise Mind already has the answer. Listen.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 484 Td (When ready, slowly walk back up the staircase.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 467 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 450 Td (MEDITATION SCRIPT 2: STONE ON THE LAKE) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 433 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 416 Td (Imagine you are a flat stone thrown onto a lake.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 399 Td (You skim the surface \(Emotion Mind - reactive, choppy\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 382 Td (Then you begin to sink slowly, gently, down through the water.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 365 Td (Deeper... quieter... calmer...) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 348 Td (You settle on the bottom of the lake. Still. Clear. Certain.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 331 Td (This is Wise Mind. Rest here.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 314 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 297 Td (Today I am in: [ ] Emotion Mind  [ ] Reasonable Mind  [ ] Wise Mind) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 280 Td (What does my Wise Mind say about my current situation?) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 0.5 w 72 263 m 540 263 l S Q

