BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 186.96 740 Td (DISTRESS TOLERANCE: TIPP SKILLS) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 705 Td (When emotions are at 7+ out of 10, use TIPP to bring them down FAST.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 688 Td (These work with your body's nervous system to reduce arousal.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 671 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 654 Td (T = TEMPERATURE \(Ice Diving\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 637 Td (  Hold ice cubes in hands, splash ice water on face, or hold a frozen) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 620 Td (  bag on cheeks/neck. This triggers the dive reflex and slows heart rate.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 603 Td (  Duration: 30-60 seconds. Intensity drops 2-3 points quickly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 586 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 569 Td (I = INTENSE EXERCISE) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 552 Td (  Sprint, jump, do burpees, run stairs - anything to burn adrenaline.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 535 Td (  Duration: 10-20 minutes of vigorous movement.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 518 Td (  This metabolizes stress hormones your body released.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 501 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 484 Td (P = PACED BREATHING) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 467 Td (  Breathe out LONGER than you breathe in.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 450 Td (  In for 4... Out for 6... In for 4... Out for 6...) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 433 Td (  This activates the parasympathetic \(calming\) nervous system.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 416 Td (  Duration: 5-10 minutes minimum.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 399 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 382 Td (P = PAIRED MUSCLE RELAXATION) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 365 Td (  Tense each muscle group while breathing in.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 348 Td (  Release tension while breathing out and saying 'relax' silently.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 331 Td (  Work through: hands, arms, shoulders, face, chest, stomach, legs, feet.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 314 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 297 Td (MY TIPP PLAN \(fill in before a crisis happens\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 280 Td (  Ice location: _______________________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 263 Td (  Exercise I can do quickly: ___________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 246 Td (  Breathing technique I'll use: _________________________________) Tj ET

endstream
